{"tid":272453,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【最佳位置】陳慧琳版 vs 趙學而版","createTime":"2017-06-05T23:44:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T16:13:07.000Z","uid":69568,"like":58,"dislike":127,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c50201b7b499e5d0b5b3fb1a1e65ba751879973c","tid":272453,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T23:44:31.000Z","msg":"細個嗰陣淨係聽過趙版，好後期先聽原版<br />\n一路都受到洗腦，話趙唱得好好，唔唱歌好可惜之類<br />\n但睇返歌詞，呢首歌唱到咁跳脫係好怪，原版先係唱返嗰種感覺，當然你可以話趙版係已經睇化咗啦，但始於覺得好牽強&hellip;我聽完原版之後&hellip;真心覺得感情表達得好好，不斷loop 同埋搵唔同版本聽&hellip;但趙版完全比唔到呢種感覺同埋loop 嘅衝動我，只係一首幾順耳嘅pop而已<br />\n<br />\n某程度上覺得趙版係破壞咗首歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過睇返兩登過往評價，趙版係屌打嘅，所以想了解下大家睇法<br />\n<br />\nkelly版 正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-IzkEPtgEcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-IzkEPtgEcs&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=776f1ec6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-IzkEPtgEcs</a><br />\n<br />\n趙學而版 負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-lB9Z4IeTDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-lB9Z4IeTDc&d=Rq9gFWrYpwVjoItm5vmgSSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=b1db99b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-lB9Z4IeTDc</a>"},{"pid":"4d8ca4b7699e13b8042fa69edeab3e8d4e1fe281","tid":272453,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:15:57.000Z","msg":"投完票講兩句得嗎"},{"pid":"65affd84e1dd51b49684a7b4027c58f982af67b4","tid":272453,"uid":46207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T00:22:14.000Z","msg":"打和 super!   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論你喜歡誰 請你記住留下給我這位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8b29978dcac6e425dee416f9de31ed9f56b276","tid":272453,"uid":17110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-